pageContext.claim: “The numbers are going down very substantially, without question. I mean, very powerfully going down. You look at Florida, you look at Georgia, you look at many other states -- the numbers are going down and they've been open and -- or very substantially open and pretty much completely open, in some cases.”
pageContext.analysis: This was false. For both Florida and Georgia, the number of new cases per week had remained unchanged for more than a month.
